WEBVTT
NOTE OE3D — Script1 — Hmoob

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:01.484
Nyob zoo!

2
00:00:01.434 --> 00:00:05.138
Kuv yog koj tus kws kho mob ntawm Ortho Espace 3D hauv Guyane.

3
00:00:05.138 --> 00:00:09.502
Koj lub cuab yeej kho mob yog ib yam khoom kho mob muaj nqis heev.

4
00:00:09.502 --> 00:00:13.655
Kom nws tseem ua hauj lwm zoo ntev, nov yog ob peb yam uas yuav tsum ua txhua hnub.

5
00:00:15.055 --> 00:00:16.608
Kev ntxuav.

6
00:00:16.558 --> 00:00:20.739
Nchuav koj lub cuab yeej txhua hnub nrog daim ntaub ntub me me thiab xab npum maj mam.

7
00:00:20.739 --> 00:00:22.734
Tsis txhob tso nws hauv dej.

8
00:00:22.734 --> 00:00:26.449
Cia nws qhuav hauv cua, tsis txhob nyob ze qhov kub.

9
00:00:27.849 --> 00:00:29.589
Kev hnav thiab kev txhuam.

10
00:00:29.539 --> 00:00:32.488
Ua raws li koj tus kws kho mob cov lus qhia.

11
00:00:32.488 --> 00:00:34.509
Muaj sijhawm so tsis tu ncua.

12
00:00:34.509 --> 00:00:38.971
Yog koj pom liab los yog kev txhuam txuas ntxiv, hu rau peb sai sai.

13
00:00:40.371 --> 00:00:41.963
Kev saib xyuas.

14
00:00:41.913 --> 00:00:44.480
Xyuas koj lub cuab yeej tsis tu ncua.

15
00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:48.830
Yog koj xav mob los yog tsis tau zoo, hu rau peb tam sim no.

16
00:00:50.230 --> 00:00:51.631
Kev khaws cia.

17
00:00:51.581 --> 00:00:55.194
Khaws koj lub cuab yeej kom tsis raug kub thiab ntub.

18
00:00:55.194 --> 00:00:58.185
Tsis txhob cia nws poob los yog raug ntaus.

19
00:00:59.585 --> 00:01:01.431
Kev tu lub manchon.

20
00:01:01.381 --> 00:01:05.724
Yog koj hnav lub cuab hloov, ntxuav lub manchon txhua hmo nrog dej thiab xab npum maj mam.

21
00:01:05.724 --> 00:01:08.271
Tig nws kom nws qhuav hauv cua.

22
00:01:08.271 --> 00:01:10.767
Npaj hloov tshiab txhua rau lub hlis.

23
00:01:12.167 --> 00:01:16.121
Yog muaj lus nug, peb lub pab neeg nyob ntawm xov tooj los yog WhatsApp.

24
00:01:16.071 --> 00:01:17.575
Saib xyuas koj tus kheej!
